Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.24,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:40.97,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Air Battle Over Dover
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:05.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the most beautiful\Nflower in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mrs. Hudson!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:20.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:22.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get breakfast ready right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:26.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like it soon, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already up, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It crashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:52.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:16.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The gasoline is about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:18.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary, get the mail bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:29.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:30.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was you, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:55.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn, burn it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:24.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mary, something cold?\N- Something warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:31.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,- Very well.\N- Bye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call us if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:45.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you be so casual,\Ncalling her "Mary"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mr. And Mrs. Hudson\Nand I were flying mates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying mates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:05.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Her husband, Jim was a nice young\Nman studying air plane design.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When Jim won her heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,we were all heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:20.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But within a month\Nof their marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a horrible accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:30.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After the accident,\Nshe disappeared from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:35.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the accident this morning\Nbrought back the bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to her efforts,\Nthe mail didn't get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:50.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the airmail flight, just opened\Nbetween London and Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've yet to make\Na single delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the commemorative\Nstamps were issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there's been\Na series of accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We always keep the planes\Nin good working condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the day of the flight,\Nthe planes break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the postal business\Nitself may be discontinued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return to the airport\Nand try again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if someone's\Ninterfering with those flights?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The fuel pipe has a crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A metal rasp was used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then someone's\Ndefinitely interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, do you want to race?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Honourable Count,\Nit's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:07:00.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Mary!\NI've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:07.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This highway looks sad without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:12.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That shabby looking machine\Ndoesn't suit you, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me know,\NI'll lend you my car any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's shabby?!\NYou old speed freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mary's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary, how have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You all look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Step down, step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:38.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Make room for Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really popular.\NBut I can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fly this tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This old plane's really beat-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been well cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Mary! You're here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary, Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so excited, will he\Nbe able to fly tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,\Nlet's finish the inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you fussing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes! Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:21.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes already caught wind of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Another fish from\Nthat river back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares where\Nthe fish comes from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Back river or not, it's all protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean about Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:41.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feed you meat, eggs or whatever\Nyou want soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:45.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You spent all your money\Non those commemorative stamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure they'll\Nbecome valuable soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop tomorrow's flight,\Nthe airmail business will cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, the airmail stamps\Nwill stop being issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:58.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In no time, stamp collectors\Nwill come for my stamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:02.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can name any price I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So today, I will say goodbye\Nto these fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately the odds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop yapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:17.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the river\Nand fish for my supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir! Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to someone like Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson will be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we'll keep eye on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:17.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:18.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Tommy, did you see Mr. Holmes\Nand Mr. Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me they would keep\Nan eye on the plane all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't seen\Nthem this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're having breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:48.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.\NWe had tons of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've worked throughout the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:53.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You did something with the plane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did a little more this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cliché, using nitroglycerine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it being artistic and reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:14.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The postal plane is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please postpone your flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The future of airmail\Ndepends on this flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mr. Holmes and\NMr. Watson are not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That means something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!\NThe engine's running great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on its way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not even aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last airmail flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:58.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cooked before\Nthat rope comes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:16.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever!\NIt's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't hear me over the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bomb on your plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:01.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The postal plane's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's witness the end of Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:14.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mrs. Hudson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!\NThere's nitroglycerine on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch that plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, stop, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:46.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, here comes Mary!\NJust like old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:02.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:09.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk!\NYou'll bite your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nitroglycerine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even make\Nan emergency landing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the plane steady.\NI'll look for the nitroglycerine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've done a lot\Nof sabotage to this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something like wire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this for emergency repair!\NBut I can't take my hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:44.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:45.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:49.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's desperately trying to repair it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last desperate struggle\Nof Detective Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep struggling in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The game's over!\NIt's going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:34.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hold up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it seems he's repaired\Nit for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop struggling\Nand start crashing, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we will after I find\Nthe nitroglycerine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:03.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know where it's hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll get mad if I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:16.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Goodness!\NThey're still flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, w... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The old speed freak again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Honourable Count, could you please\Nlet me borrow your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what an irresistible line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:40.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be my guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even care if you wreck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:43.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, dynamic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you found it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's not in the body,\Nit must be somewhere in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, he's checking the wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive he can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's close! He's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:34.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smarty Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving up on this perfect crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm moving onto brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to rip us\Napart with the anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:56.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the nitroglycerine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not so bad yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you\Ncan kick it with bare feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on pulling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:01.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to come\Napart in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:05.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, give me the pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nitroglycerine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, Mr. Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump onto the bag, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:12.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:13.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Dover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of airmail flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out who the culprit was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't undervalued the planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a thrill that was, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:25.85,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hip hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.75,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hip hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.66,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hip hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.42,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hip hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're having\Nfish from the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:38.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feed you tons of meat someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:45.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Commemorative stamps for the\Nsubway opening will be issued!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:51.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:54.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be eating fish from\Nthe park for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, they had the first airmail\Nflight after the grand reopening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:20.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it's flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:21.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:24.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.42,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitled Version Produced by\NPIONEER ENTERTAINMENT (USA) INC.\NIn association with\NNEW GENERATION PICTURES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.49,0:23:45.46,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Producer\NHENRY GOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:47.50,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:49.53,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitlers\NBRETT JACOBSEN, DIANA TOLIN,\NAKI MATSUMOTO & MAKOTO SHIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:00.14,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon the request for an investigation\Nby the wealthy Mr. Gilmore...
